You mean you don't regret what you did?

242
00:15:35,517 --> 00:15:40,064
I mean, is there even any point
to classic literature?

243
00:15:40,147 --> 00:15:43,567
These days, AI can draw pictures
and make videos.

244
00:15:43,651 --> 00:15:46,820
