00:41:40,372 --> 00:41:41,373
Miss Oe?

623
00:41:42,458 --> 00:41:43,751
What is it?

624
00:41:47,338 --> 00:41:48,797
This must be the moment

625
00:41:50,007 --> 00:41:52,801
